description:
Thoughts?

A few weeks ago @DavidNinoRodriguezOfficial put out this groundbreaking video notifying people on a wide variety of topics ranging from #PedoGate, #PizzaGate, #SpiritCooking and even speaks on some of his efforts to #StopHumanTrafficking.

We will be having him on @Factions_Of_Freedom this week to speak on the collapse of Hollywood, pedophiles being exposed and even touching on approaches and responses to the coronavirus as well as our lives after lockdown. We’ll be talking about these transformative times and more!
